VALUES(2734, 'But Dumbledore...', 102, 1, 30);
VALUES(2735, 'Dumbledore has already... risked enough on my behalf. Besides, people like me are... Well, let''s just say that I''m used to it by now.', 102, 11, 30);
VALUES(2736, 'Why do you look so miserable, Harry?', 102, 11, 30);
VALUES(2737, 'None of it made any difference. Pettigrew escaped.', 102, 1, 30);
VALUES(2738, 'Didn''t make any difference? Harry it made all the difference in the world. You have uncovered the truth. You saved an innocent man from a terrible fate. It made a great deal of difference. If I am proud of anything... it is of how much you have learned this year. Now, since I am no longer your teacher... I feel no guilt whatsoever about giving this back to you. So now I''ll say goodbye, Harry. I feel sure we''ll meet again sometime. Until then... mischief managed.', 102, 11, 30);
VALUES(2739, 'Stand back, I said! Or I''ll take it upstairs if you don''t settle.', 103, 2, 36);
