VALUES(3452, 'I dunno. It was like I''d fallen into one of my dreams. One of my nightmares.', 129, 1, 30);
VALUES(3453, 'Were there others? In the graveyard, were there others?', 129, 13, 30);
VALUES(3454, 'Um. I don''t think I said anything about a graveyard Professor.', 129, 1, 30);
VALUES(3455, 'Marvellous creatures dragons aren''t they? Do you think that miserable oaf would have led you into the woods if I hadn''t suggested it? Do you think Cedric Diggory would have told you to hold the egg under the water if I hadn''t have told him first myself? Do you think Neville Longbottom the witless wonder could have provided you with gilliweed if I hadn''t have given him the book that led you straight to it? Huh??', 129, 13, 30);
VALUES(3456, 'It was you from the beginning. You put my name in the goblet of fire. You bewitched Krum. But...', 129, 1, 30);
VALUES(3457, 'You won because I made it so Potter. You ended up in that graveyard tonight because it was meant to be so. And now the deed is done. The blood that runs through these veins runs within the dark lord. Imagine how he will reward me when he learns that I have once and for all silenced the great Harry Potter.', 129, 13, 30);
VALUES(3458, 'Severus...', 129, 4, 30);
