VALUES(5885, 'Wha''?  One of us?  Tha''s mad.  I''d wager me life it wasn'' none of you lot.  An'' if it was me I''d kno'', wouldn'' I?  Talk in me sleep on occasion, I''ll admit, but there''s only Fang aroun'' ter hear an'' mostly it''s gibberish an'' besides I''d cut me tongue out ''fore ''d betray ''arry e''en in me dreams --', 188, 5, 17);
